pair.value: The Handle Service Request process addresses the whole case to resolution. Its approach is as follows:1) Assign case to Case Worker2) Case Worker will resolve case and update status accordingly in the following ways: 2.1 Independently solving the issue 2.2 Requesting additional details from requester 2.3 Involving more or reassigning case to other case workers3) Each Update will result in notifications to requester in both Tempo and email4) Email replies from Requester will be logged.5) Requester may re-open case.
